snippet.title: Steep
snippet.description:
Hello everyone, welcome to my channel! My name is Steep, I am a Content Creator who loves playing all types of video games and interacting with you while I do it! Come stop by my live streams where tons of people just like you can hang out and have fun! Lets do this!

Steep learning curves, chaotic results.

If this is up your alley, join the community and come participate with us! 
___________
PC Specs:
CPU: i7-8700K 3.70GHz
GPU: NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1070 Ti
RAM: 32GB
Webcam: Logitech C615
Mouse: Razer Naga
Joystick: Saitek X52 PRO
___________
Feel free to join me on my Live Streams: https://www.twitch.tv/steepfrugut
